em_assets/steam/apps/3065920/extras/94c9e2c90553a294763bc9eb8f6bd971.mp4?t=1726210630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Death Is Beginning</h2>If you die in a fight, the weapon is also lost with all the runes inlay. Your can start another challenge and if lucky enough, you could find the lost weapon.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Permanent Upgrade</h2>Win or lose, when you reborn back to heaven, all the gems you collect along the way will turn to dust. Make use of these dust to unlock permanent upgrade.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065920/extras/ca840b2f7b1dcee0ffd3f86197d542f0.avif?t=1726210630\" width=600 height=323 /></span>",
